            "creation_date": 1349213910,
            "body": "<p>You need to change your OnShowMeUrCode() function to be public, not private.  Since it's part of the Activity class, your Button won't have access to it if it's private.<\/p>\n\n<p>Plus it's in the docs:\n<a href=\"http://developer.android.com/reference/android/widget/Button.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://developer.android.com/reference/android/widget/Button.html<\/a><\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 12698753,
            "question_id": 12698487
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/e1d3ef7ad6fddbd15a442f2ab679109f?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
                "account_id": 398659,
